<p>
  I thought it might be informative to put the three English versions
  of the passage side by side: mine, James Legge's and Thomas Merton's.
  Here I remind the reader that Thomas Merton's version is not a translation,
  but a "free interpretative reading" based on the translations
  of James Legge and others.
</p>

